msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid ""
"Whenever possible, you can update your personal Information directly within your account settings section. Ecovac says that in certain circumstances you have the right to request the deletion of "
"Personal Information held about you, but those circumstances are never mentioned in the policy."
msgstr ""

